## Third-Party Components

This project depends on the following open-source components:

### PostgreSQL
- **URL**: https://www.postgresql.org/
- **License**: PostgreSQL License (MIT-style)
- **Version**: 18+
- **Usage**: Core database engine

### pgvector — Vector Similarity Search for PostgreSQL
- **GitHub**: https://github.com/pgvector/pgvector
- **License**: Apache License 2.0
- **Version**: 0.8.2+
- **Usage**: VECTOR type, HNSW index, cosine similarity operators

### Apache AGE — Apache Graph Extension
- **URL**: https://age.apache.org/
- **License**: Apache License 2.0
- **Version**: 1.7.0+
- **Usage**: Property graph support, Cypher query language, graph traversal

### pg-embedding-gen-by-yhw — In-Database Embedding Generation
- **Author**: Haiwen Yin (尹海文)
- **GitHub**: https://github.com/Haiwen-Yin/pg-embedding-gen-by-yhw
- **License**: Apache License 2.0
- **Version**: 0.2.0+
- **Usage**: Custom PG18 extension for SQL-callable embedding generation via COPY FROM PROGRAM + Python proxy; calls any OpenAI-compatible /v1/embeddings API
- **Note**: NOT a built-in PostgreSQL feature; requires separate installation

### psycopg2 — PostgreSQL Adapter for Python
- **URL**: https://www.psycopg.org/
- **License**: GNU LGPL v3 (psycopg2) / Apache License 2.0 (psycopg2-binary)
- **Version**: 2.8.6+
- **Usage**: Python database driver, ThreadedConnectionPool

### BGE-M3 Embedding Model (FlagEmbedding)
- **GitHub**: https://github.com/FlagOpen/FlagEmbedding
- **License**: Apache License 2.0 (MIT-style for model weights)
- **Model**: BAAI/bge-m3
- **Usage**: Text embedding generation (1024 dimensions), served via vLLM / LM Studio

### Python `requests` Library
- **URL**: https://docs.python-requests.org/
- **License**: Apache License 2.0
- **Usage**: HTTP client for pg-embedding-gen-by-yhw proxy

### HNSW Algorithm
- **Paper**: Efficient and Robust Approximate Nearest Neighbor Search Using Hierarchical Navigable Small World Graphs
- **Authors**: Yuivii A. Malkov, Dmitry A. Yashunin
- **URL**: https://arxiv.org/abs/1603.09320
- **Usage**: Algorithm reference for pgvector HNSW index implementation

